4
00:01:40,450 --> 00:01:44,710
[One day ago]

5
00:01:41,990 --> 00:01:44,710
Shi Si, have you made up your mind

6
00:01:44,940 --> 00:01:46,430
to marry Mo Yan in my place?

7
00:01:49,300 --> 00:01:50,500
I have.

8
00:01:51,250 --> 00:01:52,880
If doing this can make you and Sikong be together,

9
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:54,479
I'm willing to do it.

10
00:01:57,250 --> 00:01:58,380
Do you know

11
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,440
what marriage means?

12
00:02:03,390 --> 00:02:04,480
Being a wife

13
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:13,760
means living with someone every day,

14
00:02:14,780 --> 00:02:16,550
even spending the rest of your life together.

15
00:02:20,250 --> 00:02:21,700
If you don't love this person,

16
00:02:23,090 --> 00:02:24,210
your life

17
00:02:25,650 --> 00:02:27,250
could be very painful.

18
00:02:33,060 --> 00:02:34,220
It's okay.

19
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:36,120
Back then,

20
00:02:36,590 --> 00:02:38,329
you saved me and brought me back to the Xuanyuan family.

21
00:02:38,970 --> 00:02:40,680
I lost my memory.

22
00:02:41,630 --> 00:02:43,190
As someone without a past,

23
00:02:45,410 --> 00:02:47,120
I have no right to love,

24
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,730
and I don't expect anyone to love me.

25
00:02:57,780 --> 00:02:58,820
If one day,

26
00:02:59,810 --> 00:03:01,210
you find someone you love,

27
00:03:02,540 --> 00:03:04,740
and this marriage becomes a restriction to you,

28
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:06,540
you can leave,

29
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,840
and no one can stop you.

30
00:03:11,490 --> 00:03:13,640
[Bailing Tavern]

31
00:03:16,590 --> 00:03:17,670
Do you feel like this place

32
00:03:18,710 --> 00:03:19,510
smells very good?

33
00:03:31,210 --> 00:03:32,910
This must be Mr. Mo, right?

34
00:03:33,620 --> 00:03:35,130
Seeing is believing.

35
00:03:35,390 --> 00:03:36,930
You really are a handsome and talented man.

36
00:03:39,420 --> 00:03:40,180
Sorry for bothering you.

37
00:03:40,829 --> 00:03:42,410
I was really scared yesterday.

38
00:03:42,710 --> 00:03:44,100
Two groups of people started fighting here

39
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:46,110
for no reason.

40
00:03:46,350 --> 00:03:48,370
I'm just a small business owner

41
00:03:48,750 --> 00:03:50,590
trying to live a peaceful life.

42
00:03:50,710 --> 00:03:52,230
I didn't expect my tavern to be smashed,

43
00:03:52,270 --> 00:03:54,010
and two of my staff were killed.

44
00:03:55,620 --> 00:03:57,370
Be careful!

45
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:57,990
Yes.

46
00:03:58,110 --> 00:03:58,710
Madam.

47
00:03:59,910 --> 00:04:00,750
I want to...

48
00:04:00,860 --> 00:04:02,540
Just call me Bailing.

49
00:04:03,150 --> 00:04:04,420
Misters, don't just stand there.

50
00:04:04,590 --> 00:04:05,510
Please, have a seat.

51
00:04:13,750 --> 00:04:14,510
Miss Bailing,

52
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,089
have there been

53
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,230
any suspicious people

54
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:19,430
in the tavern these past few days?

55
00:04:21,990 --> 00:04:23,950
I really can't say.

56
00:04:24,350 --> 00:04:26,560
There are people coming and going here every day.

57
00:04:26,670 --> 00:04:28,310
Xuanwu Street is right outside.

58
00:04:28,710 --> 00:04:31,480
We get all sorts of people, drinking, staying the night,

59
00:04:31,790 --> 00:04:33,720
from all classes and walks of life.

60
00:04:34,110 --> 00:04:36,730
I really don't know what you meant by suspicious.

61
00:04:44,710 --> 00:04:45,680
Mr. Mo,

62
00:04:46,390 --> 00:04:48,940
although I'm just a wine seller,

63
00:04:49,150 --> 00:04:50,810
I am aware of the reputation of the Mo family.

64
00:04:51,630 --> 00:04:52,900
Since you're here,

65
00:04:53,909 --> 00:04:55,300
could it be that the demon clan came to attack?

66
00:04:56,430 --> 00:04:57,740
Don't worry.

67
00:04:57,990 --> 00:04:59,040
During times of peace,

68
00:04:59,300 --> 00:05:00,630
the Mo family not only hunts demons

69
00:05:00,710 --> 00:05:02,340
but also handles ordinary matters.

70
00:05:03,950 --> 00:05:05,150
Thank you for your assistance today.

71
00:05:05,470 --> 00:05:06,540
We will take our leave now.

72
00:05:11,390 --> 00:05:13,180
Take care.

73
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:17,260
Master went out today.

74
00:06:17,660 --> 00:06:19,180
As the Madam of the house,

75
00:06:19,210 --> 00:06:20,800
I will be the one to accept the tea from the new bride.

76
00:06:23,220 --> 00:06:24,910
I heard that Yan

77
00:06:25,450 --> 00:06:27,360
spent the last night in the study.

78
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:31,090
This was your fault as the wife.

79
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:36,550
The wedding night is a joyous occasion in one's life.

80
00:06:37,470 --> 00:06:39,760
How could you sleep separately from your husband?

81
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:43,500
This is a sign of discord between husband and wife.

82
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:47,070
Xuanyuan Yu!

83
00:06:50,290 --> 00:06:51,380
Second Madam,

84
00:06:51,510 --> 00:06:53,780
have you heard anything else? Feel free to say them all.

85
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,490
Funny you should ask.

86
00:06:55,530 --> 00:06:57,360
There is indeed an interesting story.

87
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:59,700
The daughter of the Xuanyuan family

88
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:02,020
is truly spontaneous.

89
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:04,160
The young master of the Sikong family

90
00:07:04,190 --> 00:07:06,440
must be a remarkable young man.

91
00:07:06,590 --> 00:07:09,910
Otherwise, why would you be so enamored with him?

92
00:07:10,770 --> 00:07:13,090
You are entangled with another man.

93
00:07:13,110 --> 00:07:15,000
With such improper conduct,

94
00:07:16,630 --> 00:07:18,150
I'm afraid it will be difficult for you

95
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:20,140
to become the future Madam of the Mo family.

96
00:07:20,270 --> 00:07:21,280
Second Madam,

97
00:07:21,860 --> 00:07:24,090
I'm not very interested

98
00:07:24,110 --> 00:07:25,230
in the position of the Madam.

99
00:07:25,970 --> 00:07:28,470
But I found you've been longing for this vacant position for many years.

100
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:31,070
Why don't you go up and try it yourself?

101
00:07:31,820 --> 00:07:32,390
You...

102
00:07:43,210 --> 00:07:44,200
Second Madam,

103
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,780
I'm different from you.

104
00:07:45,860 --> 00:07:48,180
I always speak my mind.

105
00:07:48,250 --> 00:07:49,730
I will always call you Second Madam,

106
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:51,280
without missing a single word.

107
00:07:51,730 --> 00:07:54,790
I heard that my husband's birth mother, Madam Ye,

108
00:07:54,820 --> 00:07:56,590
has long since left the mansion.

109
00:07:56,740 --> 00:07:58,350
So I won't embarrass myself

110
00:07:58,360 --> 00:08:00,090
by serving you as my mother-in law.

111
00:08:00,780 --> 00:08:01,490
Furthermore,

112
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,400
while I

113
00:08:02,430 --> 00:08:04,050
may not know much,

114
00:08:04,230 --> 00:08:05,510
I do understand

115
00:08:05,710 --> 00:08:06,550
the simple principle

116
00:08:06,570 --> 00:08:07,690
of not meddling in affairs

117
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,640
beyond one's station.

118
00:08:10,420 --> 00:08:13,400
As the Master's concubine and second wife for many years,

119
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:16,360
you may not be well-versed in marital relationships.

120
00:08:16,380 --> 00:08:18,330
Therefore, I won't trouble you for advice.

121
00:08:28,950 --> 00:08:29,950
Don't worry.

122
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:32,190
There are many ways to deal with her.

123
00:08:34,510 --> 00:08:35,450
Where is Dongling?

124
00:08:35,870 --> 00:08:36,679
Call him over.

125
00:08:37,390 --> 00:08:37,909
Yes.

126
00:08:43,350 --> 00:08:45,940
My Lady, you're quite daring.

127
00:08:46,030 --> 00:08:48,030
Your words just now were indeed impressive,

128
00:08:48,070 --> 00:08:50,540
but you've just married into the Mo family and already offended the Madam.

129
00:08:50,990 --> 00:08:52,570
Will our days ahead

130
00:08:52,660 --> 00:08:54,020
be difficult?

131
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:56,360
People like her

132
00:08:56,380 --> 00:08:57,930
don't need to be pleased,

133
00:08:58,300 --> 00:09:00,710
and I don't know how to please her anyway.

134
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:04,980
But how did you know about the situation in the Mo family?

135
00:09:05,750 --> 00:09:07,170
Before I got married,

136
00:09:07,270 --> 00:09:08,470
Yu told me

137
00:09:09,430 --> 00:09:12,140
that Second Madam is not Mo Yan's birth mother

138
00:09:12,350 --> 00:09:14,330
but always exerts her authority as his mother.

139
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,420
I guess

140
00:09:15,730 --> 00:09:17,140
Mo Yan is not having a good time either.

141
00:09:18,130 --> 00:09:20,060
So you're not stupid, My Lady.

142
00:09:21,770 --> 00:09:23,360
I just don't keep things in mind.

143
00:09:23,410 --> 00:09:25,560
Yes, you will remember.

144
00:09:35,900 --> 00:09:39,010
My Lady, animals really like you.

145
00:09:40,270 --> 00:09:41,110
Of course.

146
00:09:50,140 --> 00:09:51,180
Mo Dongling?

147
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,950
Are you eavesdropping on us?

148
00:09:54,180 --> 00:09:55,510
Who do you think you are?

149
00:09:56,260 --> 00:09:58,450
How dare you call me by my name?

150
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:01,860
So what's your nickname?

151
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,090
My nickname is Dongdong.

152
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:04,280
Dongdong.

153
00:10:07,540 --> 00:10:08,500
Listen.

154
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,650
My brother will never like you.

155
00:10:13,460 --> 00:10:15,090
Even though you're...

156
00:10:15,640 --> 00:10:16,340
not bad-looking,

157
00:10:17,750 --> 00:10:19,650
you're just a country bumpkin,

158
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,290
not suitable for the upper class.

159
00:10:22,570 --> 00:10:25,110
How do you know for sure that I would like him?

160
00:10:25,580 --> 00:10:26,030
You...

161
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:27,920
You don't like my brother,

162
00:10:28,250 --> 00:10:30,150
but you like that Sikong Shaoyun?

163
00:10:30,180 --> 00:10:31,870
I think you are really blind.

164
00:10:35,790 --> 00:10:36,490
Brother!

165
00:10:37,050 --> 00:10:38,540
You finally came, Brother.

166
00:10:38,690 --> 00:10:39,370
Let me tell you, just now...

167
00:10:39,390 --> 00:10:39,870
Shut up.

168
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:46,800
Brother!

169
00:10:47,510 --> 00:10:49,420
Are you mad at me, Brother?

170
00:10:52,630 --> 00:10:53,310
Honey...

171
00:11:03,790 --> 00:11:04,390
Brother!

172
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:12,550
Oh no, My Lady.

173
00:11:12,650 --> 00:11:14,750
Young Master must have heard the rumor.

174
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:17,840
And just now,

175
00:11:17,950 --> 00:11:19,550
you offended him again.

176
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:31,240
She actually said she doesn't like me?

177
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:34,640
Does that really matter?

178
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,720
She actually said she doesn't like you?

179
00:11:40,490 --> 00:11:42,860
Ridiculous, absolutely absurd!

180
00:11:43,680 --> 00:11:46,170
I haven't pursued the matter between her and Sikong Shaoyun yet.

181
00:11:46,850 --> 00:11:49,240
Now that she's still in the Mo family, how dare she?

182
00:11:52,560 --> 00:11:53,340
Yan,

183
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,970
the rumor is indeed unpleasant.

184
00:11:56,590 --> 00:11:57,940
In my opinion,

185
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:59,280
you shouldn't

186
00:12:00,380 --> 00:12:01,820
have married her.

187
00:12:06,430 --> 00:12:07,460
I've thought it over.

188
00:12:07,830 --> 00:12:09,300
The situation with the demon clan is unclear at the moment.

189
00:12:09,570 --> 00:12:11,230
We may need the Xuanyuan family's strength.

190
00:12:12,140 --> 00:12:13,420
I made a pact with my father, within two years,

191
00:12:13,460 --> 00:12:14,420
to retrieve Gan Jiang

192
00:12:14,790 --> 00:12:15,710
and kill Shuo Tian.

193
00:12:16,780 --> 00:12:17,710
By then,

194
00:12:18,090 --> 00:12:18,980
she can do whatever she wants.

195
00:12:23,700 --> 00:12:25,070
What do you think about

196
00:12:26,350 --> 00:12:27,040
the innkeeper?

197
00:12:28,930 --> 00:12:31,580
I didn't notice anything unusual about her.

198
00:12:32,400 --> 00:12:33,390
She smells

199
00:12:33,690 --> 00:12:34,530
very fragrant.

200
00:12:35,470 --> 00:12:36,670
Unusually fragrant.

201
00:12:37,010 --> 00:12:38,400
Now that you mentioned it,

202
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:40,530
there is something strange about it.

203
00:12:44,390 --> 00:12:46,810
If the innkeeper is really possible to be from the demon clan,

204
00:12:47,350 --> 00:12:47,990
then they

205
00:12:48,590 --> 00:12:50,810
must have used some method to conceal the demon clan's aura.

206
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:55,430
They

207
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:56,950
might have come prepared.

208
00:12:59,250 --> 00:13:00,510
I'll go back there immediately.

209
00:13:00,870 --> 00:13:01,470
This time,

210
00:13:02,040 --> 00:13:03,100
we must not let them go.

211
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:05,650
