212
00:13:05,880 --> 00:13:07,060
We need to plan carefully.

213
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:08,120
It's been three years.

214
00:13:08,820 --> 00:13:10,500
If the demon clan really comes back,

215
00:13:11,860 --> 00:13:13,050
