261
00:14:54,260 --> 00:14:54,890
Is that so?

262
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:55,830
[Wedding]

263
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:57,990
[Wedding]

264
00:14:58,230 --> 00:14:59,430
Just you wait!

