269
00:15:16,390 --> 00:15:17,120
Lan,

270
00:15:17,550 --> 00:15:19,820
you are a descendant of the human race and the dragon race,

271
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:21,370
but you are not of the demon clan.

272
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:24,250
You are my family.

273
00:15:25,220 --> 00:15:27,780
You care for the people more than many humans.

274
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:31,540
Every banner on Xuanwu Street

275
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:32,720
