276
00:15:34,580 --> 00:15:35,820
Originally, it was nothing.

277
00:15:35,950 --> 00:15:37,980
Your comforting made me feel weak.

278
00:15:42,750 --> 00:15:44,220
When we were young, every time you cried,

279
00:15:44,500 --> 00:15:45,890
it was me who comforted you.

280
00:15:46,680 --> 00:15:48,050
You don't have to worry too much about me.

281
00:15:49,560 --> 00:15:50,370
I'm fine.

282
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:08,000
How do you know for sure that I would like him?

283
00:16:08,550 --> 00:16:09,070
Lan,

284
00:16:10,290 --> 00:16:12,410
